## Pacemaker resource ${metric.label.resource} is in status `Stopped` on ${metric.label.node}

The resource agent ${metric.label.resource} in Pacemaker HA cluster for SAP system ${metric.label.sid} has been in status `Stopped` for over 3 minutes and has failed to restart. Manual intervention is required to retry start attempts.

### Resolution

1. Access the Pacemaker cluster on ${metric.label.node}

1. Follow the [**Troubleshooting high-availability configurations for SAP**](https://cloud.google.com/solutions/sap/docs/troubleshooting/troubleshooting-sap-ha#resource_agent_is_stopped) troubleshooting guide
